            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><strong>What's new</strong><ul>
<li>Startup wizard that opens a bundled install script in Terminal or links to python.org when Python 3.8+ is missing</li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong>Improvements</strong><ul>
<li>Python scanner discovery checks Homebrew, system, and python.org framework installs and validates version 3.8 or newer</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
]]></description>
