        <item>
            <title>0.5.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2026 06:59:42 +1000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>5000</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.5.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><strong>What's new</strong><ul>
<li>Bundled Python scanner for Phase 1 volume indexing with JSON progress streaming into the existing UI</li>
<li>Scanner log panel on the dashboard with an Open in Terminal action to tail verbose scan output</li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong>Improvements</strong><ul>
<li>Version update checks run at most once per day while the main window is open and the app is in the foreground — not at startup or when only the menu bar is active</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
]]></description>
