        <item>
            <title>0.4.1</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2026 06:54:09 +1000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>4001</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.4.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><strong>What's new</strong><ul>
<li>Choose internal and external drives individually for menu bar free-space readouts (for example, HD 12GB or 6 2.8TB)</li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong>Improvements</strong><ul>
<li>Removed remaining-percentage menu bar option</li>
<li>Health menu bar icon shows condition with score, for example Fair (50)</li>
<li>System status top CPU and memory lists use full application names from Activity Monitor</li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong>Fixes</strong><ul>
<li>Top CPU and memory process names no longer truncate to short comm labels like Cu or Library</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
]]></description>
